{"tid":2334024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一田百貨沙田店即日起復業","createTime":"2020-12-21T01:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T04:06:27.000Z","uid":10540,"like":8,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"001d6c9ccf0971e29cb7eea5a08c8ac685870b9a","tid":2334024,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"昨日有4宗個案與沙田一田百貨相關。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一田仲派$20現金劵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>第四波疫情仍然嚴峻，較早前一田百貨沙田店多名員工確診，因而需要停業。一田宣布，沙田店今日起（20日）重新投入服務，而在復業前已完成多項抗疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n 一田表示，沙田店關閉期間，店內持續進行多次全面深層抗疫消毒清潔，除了在獲通報有員工確診後翌日，已主動要求及安排該店員工進行核酸檢查， 沙田店全部員工在日前（18 日）也獲安排額外進行快速檢測一次，員工的檢測報告必須為陰性才可重返工作崗位。<br />\n<br />\n沙田店重新投入服務後，所有員工，包括一田員工、一田寫字樓、貨倉員工、專櫃職員、商品推廣員及外判清潔及保安員，每隔14天必須再進行一次快速檢測，檢測報告同樣必須為陰性才可工作。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2833215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2833215&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=0b31669b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2833215</a>"},{"pid":"0777002f12d408c4772aa5da8841ab79513290ae","tid":2334024,"uid":247896,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"說好的減少人流呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0241002dcd69053ccb96ac3a62bb90f454852eff","tid":2334024,"uid":375706,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:18:09.000Z","msg":"藍店不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e738c5a1d029c2c9d5b3b7228e046bf5242dcef5","tid":2334024,"uid":59586,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:19:25.000Z","msg":"是但啦 快D爆多幾百單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c5e63542446e3f226cbcc49b7b8318435018f2","tid":2334024,"uid":8014,"like":12,"dislike":0,